{
  "id": "adv_bond_chs_01_05",
  "title": "白石千紗5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "（ここの振り付け、どうしてもクセが出ちゃうなぁ）\n（もっと練習しないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This choreography‚ my habits keep coming out）\n（I need to practice more…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7000
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、お疲れ様。千紗も自主練？\n良かったら一緒にやらない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good work. Are you practicing on your own too‚ Chisa?\nIf you'd like‚ why don't we do it together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6519274394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですか？\nぜひお願いします……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?\nI'd love to‚ please…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1459411621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……それにしても千紗、本当に成長したわね\n最初に会った頃とは比べ物にならないくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… Anyway‚ Chisa‚ you've really grown\nbeyond comparison to when we first met.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4553970655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？\nえへへ、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that true?\nEhehe‚ thank you so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.286641407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "あと、自信もついてきたんじゃない？\n昔だったら、私が練習に誘っても断っていそうだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you've gained quite a bit of confidence‚ haven't you?\nIn the past‚ you might have declined my invitation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2893398762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……瑠依さんの練習を邪魔しちゃ悪いって\n断っちゃってたかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true… I might have refused‚\nthinking I'd be in your way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3531040669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はまだまだですから\nもし気になったことがあったらビシバシ言って下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I still have a long way to go.\nIf you notice anything‚ please tell me strictly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6590223153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、向上心があっていいわね\nそれじゃあ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I like your ambition.\nWell then――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0849631468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "――っていう感じかしら\nいい出来だけど、まだまだ伸びしろはあるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That's about it‚ I think.\nYou did well‚ but there’s still room for improvement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8824689388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "はい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3602015654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗……？\nごめんなさい、言い方がキツかったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ch-Chisa…?\nI'm sorry‚ was I being too harsh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5387502629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　いえいえいえ！　むしろ優しかったです\n優しくて、その……逆にそわそわしちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? No‚ no‚ no! You were actually quite kind.\nSo kind that‚ um… it actually made me a bit restless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1896830677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんは、もっともっと厳しくって\nそれに慣れちゃってるからか、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan is much‚ much stricter than that.\nMaybe I've just gotten used to it‚ um…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1850814621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "それなりに厳しく言ったつもりなんだけど\n怜はいつも、どんな言い方をしているのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I was being strict in my own way.\nI wonder how Rei usually talks to you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9502528946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "でも……分かったわ。千紗がそうしてほしいなら\n私も挑戦してみる。もう一度踊ってくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I understand. If that's what you want‚\nI'll try it too. Will you dance for me once more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5247199496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "怜みたいに……怜みたいに……。よし……！\nそこの動き！　流れでごまかさないの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like Rei… like Rei…. Alright…!\nThat movement right there! Don't just gloss over it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1789604307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "まだまだいけるでしょ！\n――踊れ！　踊れ！　どんどん踊れっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can do better than that!\n――Dance! Dance! Keep dancing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6947254618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依さん、私のために厳しくしてくれてる、けど……）\n（あれ？　な、なんか変な気が……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rui-san is being strict for me‚ but…）\n（Wait? Something feels a bit off…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1357007146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "まだよ！　まだよ！　どんどん踊れっ！\nグミ！　グミ！　グミ！　コーラ味っっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not yet! Not yet! Keep dancing!\nGummy! Gummy! Gummy! Cola flavor!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0557685336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_chs_01_05-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "（こ、これ、ただのアレンジした）\n（モノマネになってるよ～～！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Th-this is just a weirdly arranged）\n（impersonation~~!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0567206185,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}